<h1>Welcome to MyTrail</h1>

<h2>A fun and easy way to track your Scouting advancement.</h2>

You can use this application to track your camping trips and see all of the camping activity across the troop.<br>
You can also update the Merit badge records for you or any Scout in the troop and see all of the recent Merit badges earned across the Troop.<br><br>

Sign Up or Login to begin.
